sqlQuery.sqlText:
select empl, ctime from
( select 28800 Ctime from dual union select 29700 from dual union select 30600 from dual union select 31500 from dual union select 32400 from dual union select 33300 from dual union select 34200 from dual union select 35100 from dual union select 36000 from dual union select 36900 from dual union select 37800 from dual union select 38700 from dual union select 39600 from dual union select 40500 from dual union select 41400 from dual union select 42300 from dual union select 43200 from dual union select 44100 from dual union select 45000 from dual union select 45900 from dual union select 46800 from dual union select 47700 from dual union select 48600 from dual union select 49500 from dual union select 50400 from dual union select 51300 from dual union select 52200 from dual union select 53100 from dual union select 54000 from dual union select 54900 from dual union select 55800 from dual union select 56700 from dual union select 57600 from dual union select 58500 from dual union select 59400 from dual union select 60300 from dual ) A
INNER JOIN
(SELECT cre_person EMPL FROM r5crewemployees where cre_crew = #prompt('SEL_CREW')#) B
ON 1=1
where not exists (select 'x' from (select 'MARIE' EMP, '107625' WO, 30600 STTIME, 39600 ETIME FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'MARIE', '141633', 39600, 43200 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'MARIE', '188312', 45000, 59400 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'AMERIGO', '213001', 28800, 37800 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'AMERIGO', '225871', 37800, 45000 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'AMERIGO', '230009', 47700, 60300 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'ISAAC', '213298', 28800, 39600 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'ISAAC', '225804', 39600, 45000 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'ISAAC', '230165', 47700, 52200 FROM DUAL UNION SELECT 'ISAAC', '230163', 54000, 63000 FROM DUAL
union select cre_person, acs_event, acs_starttime, acs_endtime from r5crewemployees inner join R5ACTSCHEDULES on acs_responsible = cre_person where trunc(sysdate) = trunc(acs_sched) and cre_crew = #prompt('SEL_CREW')#) c where a.CTIME between sttime and etime - 1 and empl = emp )

sqlQuery.name: SQL-SUB-3
sqlQuery.sqlText:
select cre_person, ctime, case when ctime between boo_on and boo_off - 1 then boo_event else 'FREE' end workstatus
from ( select 28800 Ctime from dual union select 29700 from dual union select 30600 from dual union select 31500 from dual union select 32400 from dual union select 33300 from dual union select 34200 from dual union select 35100 from dual union select 36000 from dual union select 36900 from dual union select 37800 from dual union select 38700 from dual union select 39600 from dual union select 40500 from dual union select 41400 from dual union select 42300 from dual union select 43200 from dual union select 44100 from dual union select 45000 from dual union select 45900 from dual union select 46800 from dual union select 47700 from dual union select 48600 from dual union select 49500 from dual union select 50400 from dual union select 51300 from dual union select 52200 from dual union select 53100 from dual union select 54000 from dual union select 54900 from dual union select 55800 from dual union select 56700 from dual union select 57600 from dual union select 58500 from dual union select 59400 from dual union select 60300 from dual ) A, r5crewemployees, r5bookedhours, r5actschedules where acs_responsible = cre_person and boo_person = cre_person and boo_event = acs_event and boo_act = acs_activity and trunc(sysdate) = trunc(acs_sched) and cre_crew = #prompt('SEL_CREW')# and ctime between least(boo_on, acs_starttime) and greatest(boo_off, acs_endtime) - 1

sqlQuery.name: SQL2
sqlQuery.sqlText:
select cre_person "Employee", swork "Scheduled Work", sloc "Location", evt_code "Nearby Work", evt_desc "Description", evt_object ||' :: '||r5rep.repgetdesc('EN','OBJ',evt_object,null,null) "Equipment", act_act "Activity" , act_trade "Trade", max(act_est) "Hours"
from
(select cre_person, ctime, case when ctime between boo_on and boo_off - 1 then boo_event else 'FREE' end workstatus, evt_code swork, evt_location sloc
from ( select 28800 Ctime from dual union select 29700 from dual union select 30600 from dual union select 31500 from dual union select 32400 from dual union select 33300 from dual union select 34200 from dual union select 35100 from dual union select 36000 from dual union select 36900 from dual union select 37800 from dual union select 38700 from dual union select 39600 from dual union select 40500 from dual union select 41400 from dual union select 42300 from dual union select 43200 from dual union select 44100 from dual union select 45000 from dual union select 45900 from dual union select 46800 from dual union select 47700 from dual union select 48600 from dual union select 49500 from dual union select 50400 from dual union select 51300 from dual union select 52200 from dual union select 53100 from dual union select 54000 from dual union select 54900 from dual union select 55800 from dual union select 56700 from dual union select 57600 from dual union select 58500 from dual union select 59400 from dual union select 60300 from dual union select 61200 from dual union select 62100 from dual union select 63000 from dual union select 63900 from dual) A, r5crewemployees, r5bookedhours, r5actschedules, r5events where acs_responsible = cre_person and boo_person = cre_person and boo_event = acs_event and boo_act = acs_activity and trunc(sysdate) = trunc(acs_sched) and cre_crew = #prompt('SEL_CREW')# and ctime between least(boo_on, acs_starttime) and greatest(boo_off, acs_endtime) - 1 and evt_code = boo_event ) z , r5events, r5activities where evt_location = sloc and trunc(evt_target) > trunc(sysdate) and act_event = evt_code and evt_rstatus = 'R' and workstatus = 'FREE'
group by cre_person, swork, sloc, evt_code, evt_desc, evt_object, act_act, act_trade
